      "role": "user",
      "content": "it’s just... it’s hard to talk to people about it. they all just want to tell me to \"stay positive\" or that \"it gets better,\" but they don't understand how exhausting it is. i feel like a burden to everyone. like i'm just taking up space and waiting for something to happen. it feels like there's no real point to any of it anymore.",
